processControlChangeQueueElement(ControlChangeQueueElement) - Method in class at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.CarApplication
Processes all the control-change-events (via putting an element on the CarApplication.controlChangeQueue) and updates all connections in CarApplication.connections.
If the id of passed ControlChangeQueueElement exceeds the size of CarApplication.connections or equals -1, the first GamepadConnection is set as the controlling device.
